Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:07.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}武裝偵探社員 谷崎潤一郎的謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是因為測試 但也做了相當過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫谷崎潤一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在偵探社負責類似助手的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 不用掛在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人 意外的是個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這邊這位…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谷崎的妹妹直美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是兄妹嗎 作為兄妹而言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮和臉都感覺不太像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你不信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問是血脈相連的親兄妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是這一塊 真的是一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.86,0:00:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.22,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於他們的事不要深究
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:54.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊 哥哥 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:01:03.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}敦 很識相。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.03,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂 慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 小子 你從今天起也是武裝偵探社的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.03,0:00:58.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}還要更多？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:00:59.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.28,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哥哥 直美我會加油的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要給周圍的人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做有辱偵探社名號的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好其他人也好 唯獨這兩點是貫徹始終的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 太宰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能用這纖纖玉指把我勒死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別剛說完你就給偵探社的招牌抹黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢夥總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必她出手 讓我用粗糙的手指來勒死你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:32.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}正在給偵探社的招牌抹黑的兩位偵探社前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位在加入偵探社之前是做什麼的?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我只是隨便問問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜猜看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦 這是慣例的遊戲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人要猜前輩以前的職業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 算是偵探社學習的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谷崎先生和直美小姐是 學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 猜對了 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說直美小姐是來打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為穿制服所以猜是在讀的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷崎先生因為和你年齡相仿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑直覺猜的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直說無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼國木田君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前的工作什麼的無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公務員嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在政府機關做事之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點 他原來是老師哦 數學老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡明擺著就是要用x的乘方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得非常有說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是過去的事了 我一點都不願去回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰先生是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰先生是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全想像不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢夥以前的工作 是武裝偵探社七大不可思議之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得第一個猜對的人會有賞金對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞金？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因為沒人猜對賞金已經漲得很高了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漲得很高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順…順便問一下 上漲的賞金現在到多少了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總額70萬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七十萬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜…猜中了就能拿到賞金是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:29.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}現在 身無分文的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}對眼前的七十萬賞金 燃起了鬥志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真萬確嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺主義者說話算話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦君 你的眼神變了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強大的氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七十萬 我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投機商
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工薪族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究人員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞記者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木匠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:52.67,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:53.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛行員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:54.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:54.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂說一氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:55.71,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No No
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:03:57.53,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卜卜~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:03:59.90,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:00.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:01.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我是演員人家會害羞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定是遊手好閒的無業遊民吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我是不會撒謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認輸了嗎 敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這裡的賬單就拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎——？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有現金的話 可以賒賬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是偵探社的御用餐廳“漩渦”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是谷崎 好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委託人已經到事務所了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 該幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜我曾是什麼職業的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有機會再玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:10.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖著沉重的步伐 蹣跚前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:10.78,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その重い足を膝を前へ導く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:15.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探求力量為何物 去問個究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:15.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力は何だって?Go ahead 問う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:21.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你體內滋生的衝動 便是無盡寶藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:21.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の中に生じる衝動は treasure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:25.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真實亦或虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:25.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本物か偽物か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:27.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,つれて行けよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至那幻想的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:30.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空想の彼方まで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的懈怠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕の中の怠慢よ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將它奪走也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さらってもいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢でも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只是一場夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:43.48,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,届きそうで 届かない make some noise
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:43.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似近在咫尺 又遙不可及 把氣氛炒熱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:50.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空虚な日常は輝き出すのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:50.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空虛的日常是否也能綻放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:56.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐き出すようにして前に前に漕げば
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:56.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要拼盡全力 不斷前蹬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:06:01.28,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らの未来は加速していくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:06:01.28,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必我們的未來也會加速前行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:04.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今この時が止まるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:04.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻就算停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:09.15,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この呼吸までは止められはしないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:09.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呼吸也絕不停息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:11.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,くだらない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:11.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ご褒美まだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:14.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讚詞何在？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞您有事想要調查 請問是調查什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若睡蓮的花朵一般夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹人憐愛的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我一起殉情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚擾到您了 請不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉剛才的事 請繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有關本次的委託內容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起 這種狀態下還能若無其事地繼續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們公司大廈的後面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有絕非善類的傢夥聚集在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕非善類的傢夥是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一群穿得破破爛爛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面還有人會說陌生的外語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢夥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殉情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是走私犯之類的貨色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論軍警怎麼管制 還是像海蟑螂那樣冒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港灣城市的報應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果能找到不法之徒的證據 就可以去和軍警交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視現場獲取證據…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦——！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是監視這種簡單的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且走私犯基本都是溜得快的無害人群
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為你的第一份工作正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷崎 你跟他一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:08:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥去的話直美也要跟去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:08.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}對第一次任務感到緊張的 新人偵探 中島敦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於你那運氣欠佳身世不幸的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也並不是完全沒有一絲憐憫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要教你一個在這個城市活下去的訣竅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別遇到這個人 一旦遇到馬上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑手黨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 是因為沒有別的叫法才這麼稱呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以港口作為勢力範圍的兇惡犯罪組織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被稱為港口黑手黨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個城市裡的黑社會中最危險的團夥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在他們之中 那個照片上的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是連我們偵探社的成員也對付不了的危險傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼危險？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是異能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是為了殺戮而特化的相當殘忍的異能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍警察也拿他沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也不想和他交手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上撿到了公文包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琢磨著會不會是有人弄丟的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是遺失物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請在這份表格上留下您的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 好像在哪見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是軍警
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被識破了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 這傢夥就是通緝令上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這個城市的軍警
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我想問下路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:10:00.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}芥川龍之介 能力名「羅生門」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.45,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正小标宋_GBK\frz270\pos(1215,417)}第三話 橫濱 匪徒 天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz270\pos(353,100)}文豪野犬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(224,562)\a1}但抱有想看的\N願望的也不只\N有我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz270\pos(183,326)}外邊是一片沉沉的漆黑之夜。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了 接下來是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殉情 一個人是辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太宰 工作怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待上天的啟示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人就能殉情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殉情 殉情 殉情 殉情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈 那是被威脅了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇惡的黑手黨之類的 還以為會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然進了不得了的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 連我都能堅持下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是谷崎先生也是異能力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我那沒什麼用的異能力不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要過分期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不是適合戰鬥的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的能力 很棒的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美最喜歡那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美 別這樣 公共場合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲 竟然頂嘴 得意忘形的嘴是哪張嘴啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這地方讓人毛骨悚然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 真的是這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫樋口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樋口小姐 走私犯都是膽小之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以肯定會準備好逃跑的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這裡 是死胡同對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕的人從那邊過來的話 就跑不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道很失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標 就是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:50.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}港口黑手黨 樋口一葉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按計劃抓住他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好 5分鐘後我就到你那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是港口黑手黨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是港口黑手黨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 止血帶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦君 你帶止血帶了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 先清洗傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須找與謝野醫生治療
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要送到醫務室去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦君 抬腳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是戰鬥人員 這點我們已經調查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你追隨勇敢的公主去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區小混混！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把直美傷成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個季節下雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦君 退到後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢夥由我來殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的「細雪」會把降雪的空間全部變成屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身後的背景覆蓋了我的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經看不見我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看不到你 子彈也能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大錯特錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏懼死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏懼殺戮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求死之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平等逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別遇到這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦遇到馬上逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙姓芥川 和那邊的小姑娘一樣是港口黑手黨的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我一個人也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令說的是活捉人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂射一氣殺了他還怎麼交差！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個廢物 退下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活捉人虎？你們到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標本來就只有你一個 人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒在那邊的同伴 可以說是受你牽連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我才害得大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 那是你的天命 人虎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你活著就會讓周圍的人遭殃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去 飯桶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便找個地方橫屍街頭才是造福社會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 天下再大也沒有你的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天命？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅生門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自不用說 剛才是故意避開你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我的羅生門天性惡食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西都吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然目標是活捉你 但你若反抗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就奪走你的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是 我的錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我活著就會害大家不幸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦…敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人還有氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起你也是武裝偵探社的一份子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做有辱偵探社名號的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧願一死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊透頂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的動作真是不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過歸根到底還是有勇無謀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧 我的黑獸天性惡食
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西都吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從子彈射出到命中之間的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這空間本身吞噬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍也好火焰也好 只要斷絕了空間 就無法觸及到我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那豈不是沒有辦法攻擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我會遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能無理取鬧地哭泣的 只有受到父母疼愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連父母都不要了的孩子沒有資格哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直過著流離失所的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連哭泣流淚也不被允許
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得不到任何人的肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至沒有身為人的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右腳再生了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 樋口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈打不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅生門 顎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本要活捉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才撕裂的是幻象嗎？ 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅生門 叢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是偵探社的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很在意美人的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷聽了你們的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:19:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你從一開始就看穿了我的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 快起來啦 敦君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要背三個人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為能活著回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 樋口 憑你是贏不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 芥川前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰先生 這次我們先撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們港口黑手黨 一定會收下人虎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那頭人虎在黑市上有懸賞金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞金額度是七十億
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去還真是讓人高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們遲早會來拜訪偵探社
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港口黑手黨一定會奪走那七十億
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 要與武裝偵探社開戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看啊 如果你夠本事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.01,0:21:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區微小企業
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是這座城市的陰暗面其本身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎根於這座城市的政治經濟等各個領域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區十幾人的偵探社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天之內就能讓你們連人帶事務所一起灰飛煙滅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒有人違抗我們還能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事我們還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些事你比誰都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前港口黑手黨 太宰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:50.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕が僕でいられる　理由を探していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:50.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尋找著沒有迷失自我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:22:03.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの胸の中で　生きている僕がいるのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:22:03.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我還在活在你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:12.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗闇も長い坂道も　越えて行けるような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:12.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是無盡的黑暗 亦或是狹長的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕になれるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:15.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一日我定能將其跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:21.58,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それぞれに今を歩いてる僕らが笑えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.27,0:22:21.58,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能讓各自活在當下的我們展露笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:27.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きている意味を確かめ合いながら進めるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.07,0:22:27.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能互相確認生存意義的同時不斷前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:33.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名前を呼ぶよ　あなたの名前を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:33.35,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去呼喚 呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:39.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがあなたでいれるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:39.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你能繼續做你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:45.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみに暮れてあなたの涙がこぼれる時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:45.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你深陷悲傷潸然落淚之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:50.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しさに溢れて心がしぼんでく時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:50.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你萬般孤寂內心憔悴之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:56.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名前を呼ぶよ　あなたの名前を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:56.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去呼喚 呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:04.57,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕の名前を呼んでくれたみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:04.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你呼喚我的名字那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.03,0:23:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在黑社會的黑市裡 被人懸賞七十億啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.37,0:23:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎…怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港口黑手黨說不定會朝這個偵探社蜂擁而來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是招惹是非的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想你自己能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.40,0:23:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 文豪野犬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話 命運主張者的悲哀

